Anicée Shahmanesh or Anicee Schahmane (Persian: انیسه شاهمنش‎) (28 January 1953, Boulogne-Billancourt, Hauts-de-Seine – d. 11 November 2006, Boncourt, Eure-et-Loir from cancer) was a French singer and actress.
